**Practicum Homework #3: Product Design Specification (PDS)**

Security Locker for Keys/Important Documents


Executive Summary / Concepts of Operations

A wall mounted lock box that can be used to store important documents, keys or other personal effects to provide 
extra security and ease of access. This project will incorporate access control meaning a verification sensor such as a pinpad or RFID
